summary: Home fit for a dragon slaying, everything collecting player.
descriptionHtml:
Home fit for a dragon slaying, everything collecting player.

This is my first mod so please enjoy and leave feedback. 

This home is located on the eastern cliff outside Whiterun, behind Battle-Horn Farm. It has a fast travel marker so its easy to find. 

Contains 84 weapon racks, 24 Mannequins, dragon priest mask bust, everything needed for crafting, your very own fish pond, dragon priest statue, plenty of storage via chest and bookshelves.
author: DistantDeath aka JacobSuitt
